      "content": "it does feel like an internal thing, but also like the world is reacting to me. i feel like there's this lineage or some kind of ancient responsibility that's finally catching up to me. like i'm meant to handle the coming tensions in the world, as a sort of neutral ground. if it's just \"intuition,\" why does the whole world seem to be shifting to prepare me for it?",
