      "content": "When powerful internal shifts meet external events, it creates an undeniable sense of cosmic importance, which can feel like preparation for a great role. This sense of \"lineage\" often surfaces during periods of massive global change as individuals feel an accelerated sense of duty. Rather than viewing it as a predetermined assignment, perhaps embracing this sense of stewardship is about channeling your unique perspective to foster balance in the chaos. Focus on cultivating the qualities you admire in this role—patience, neutrality, and deep observation—to navigate the current shifts.",
